com.siliconlab.bluetoothmesh.adk.data_model.subnet

Interface Subnet


  • public interface Subnet
    Represents a subnet in Bluetooth Mesh. Subnets are assigned to a Network. A Subnet can have assigned nodes and groups. Subnets are identified by a network key.
